channel.title: Developer Needed
channel.description:
Hello everyone, my name is Aldric. I am interested in starting my own private server and I am in need of a decent full-time developer.
I plan on making a 317 [PI]. I plan on providing all the financial support needed. I plan on either paying you monthly and/or providing rank. I plan on staying dedicated to this server and making it successful.
I have loads of ideas and motivation to get this server up and running and make it the best it can be.
If you would like more information and/or are interested in joining please contact me through Skype.
[b]Skype: aldric.austin [/b]
